{"tid":1158181,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好唔開心","createTime":"2019-05-16T19:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T10:57:24.000Z","uid":172778,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcc548dfbd4d28305e06a198de04bc2222dca22","tid":1158181,"uid":172778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"成日鬧交<br />\n少少事就屌柒我<br />\n話我蠢，無腦，失禮人，令你無面，對我好失望<br />\n一鬧交發脾氣就好似想殺左我咁<br />\n所有野都要你啱哂，要人認錯<br />\n我真係好辛苦<br />\n你話我覺得有唔啱我可以講<br />\n我講有用咩，你只會話返我<br />\n我真係好唔開心<br />\n你話你係咁，係咁臭脾氣，唔鐘意咪走<br />\n我真係每一次都好想同你講咁我地分手啦<br />\n但我又唔捨得，我真係好辛苦<br />\n有時俾你話完，我真係覺得自己咁無用不如死左去算"},{"pid":"3f960fd3d23975f0a233c68784f37aff55d4643e","tid":1158181,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7943798fdf5ec39acfd2094d8bad1f4457da1f10","tid":1158181,"uid":214290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"不如分手啦 唔好唔捨得"},{"pid":"48b8f358e244597b262316bcb489443ac87a6ffa","tid":1158181,"uid":245803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:37:18.000Z","msg":"分咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093ab2e6d753d6a69afa36b6110e0cb629180fe4","tid":1158181,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:37:31.000Z","msg":"究竟鍾意佢啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"f8170a7cb875fc3c47183cb4821a69f0d37c5758","tid":1158181,"uid":214290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:37:40.000Z","msg":"其實個男仔都唔係好好 拿拿林分手啦 唔好唔捨得啦"},{"pid":"30828393242ce592fcfcd5e87218f71eb583db78","tid":1158181,"uid":253512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:43:10.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"eb774a9096ebc37da326606560650e6730fdace2","tid":1158181,"uid":172778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"